### /api/customer API calls

### POST to create a Customer

POST http://localhost:8080/api/customer HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json


### /api/address API calls

### GET all addresses

GET http://localhost:8080/api/address HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### GET an address by id

GET http://localhost:8080/api/address/3 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### POST to create an Address

POST http://localhost:8080/api/address HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "address_line1": "345 W Main Street",
    "address_line2": "Suite 200",
    "city": "Portland",
    "state": "Oregon",
    "zip": "97239"
}

### PUT an update to an address

PUT http://localhost:8080/api/address/3 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "address_line1": "345 W Main Street",
